[#PriceReduced] Lowered by $20K to $619K, CAMPARI is a 2019 Galeon 430 HTC located in Gulf Breeze, FL. With a reputation for quality craftsmanship, Galeon Yachts are made in Poland for both US and European markets. 🇵🇱

CAMPARI offers a 2 stateroom, 2 head layout. Additional upgrades to the vessel include:
• Seakeeper 6
• 2021 Stainless Lewmar 35# Plow Anchor + 200' G4 Chain
• Full Service Volvo D6 (351hrs) + Fischer Panda 12KW Generator (483hrs)
• Aug. 2021 Fresh Bottom Paint, Zincs, Prop Tune + PropSpeed, Hull Buff & Wax
